modName: Female ImperialGale Armor as requested by friend
summary: Little nightingale armor mod I made for friend.
descriptionHtml:
OK so here it is, ImperialGale or whatever :p

I made this quickly for my friend, im not totally happy with end result but person that wanted it likes it so mission accomplished ;)

It have one big flow - when u zoom in maximally u will see that its rather poor quality, but as long as u keep camera not zoomed in fully it should be no problem ;)

It\'s based on my \"sexy crimson nightingale\" armor so it will work only on human female
One more thing, actually 2 ...
1. there is no hood for this, i just hate this hood and prefer to not use it at all ;)
2. Please no requests as of making full cape etc for this one as it is case closed for now ;)

As always have fun ;)
author: bitzupa
